      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JACKPOT CASH (1) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at Healesville over 350m (19.93). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Ready to return to form. ETHANOL VISION (4) struggled in tougher grade last start after settling off pace at Warragul, but prior to that won comfortably by 3.5 lengths at this track (24.43) beating Valletta Pearl in a Rank Limit - Grade 5 on June 24. One of the better hopes. CRAIG KEEPING (2) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 4 lengths from the winner (25.03). The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Should be in this for a long way.",
